imple Guide To Adding Theme Options</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.wptavern.com/ian-stewarts-predictions-on-wordpress-themes-for-2012\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Ian Stewarts Predictions On WordPress Themes For 2012\">Ian Stewarts Predictions On WordPress Themes For 2012</a></li>\n</ol></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~4/O8RhxVvHwjo\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";}i:3;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:17:\"Matt: Black Radio\";s:4:\"guid\";s:21:\"http://ma.tt/?p=40018\";s:4:\"link\";s:33:\"http://ma.tt/2012/02/black-radio/\";s:11:\"description\";s:652:\"<p>Friend and HSPVA alum <a href=\"http://robertglasper.com/\">Robert Glasper&#8217;s</a> new album Black Radio is out today and has so far been well-received by <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/26/arts/music/robert-glasper-experiment-to-release-black-radio.html\">a great feature in the New York Times</a> and <a href=\"http://www.npr.org/2012/02/25/147369849/robert-glasper-a-unified-field-theory-for-black-music\">on NPR</a>. You can grab the album <a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/black-radio/id488036560\">on iTunes</a> ($7) or <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Black-Radio-Robert-Glasper-Experiment/dp/B0067Q04AM\">on Amazon</a> ($9).</p>\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Tue, 28 Feb 2012 16:32:03 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:4:\"Matt\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:652:\"<p>Friend and HSPVA alum <a href=\"http://robertglasper.com/\">Robert Glasper&#8217;s</a> new album Black Radio is out today and has so far been well-received by <a href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/26/arts/music/robert-glasper-experiment-to-release-black-radio.html\">a great feature in the New York Times</a> and <a href=\"http://www.npr.org/2012/02/25/147369849/robert-glasper-a-unified-field-theory-for-black-music\">on NPR</a>. You can grab the album <a href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/black-radio/id488036560\">on iTunes</a> ($7) or <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Black-Radio-Robert-Glasper-Experiment/dp/B0067Q04AM\">on Amazon</a> ($9).</p>\";}i:4;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:51:\"Weblog Tools Collection: Themes with a Travel Theme\";s:4:\"guid\";s:41:\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/?p=11091\";s:4:\"link\";s:73:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~3/ELZVWv8WbdE/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1876:\"<p>I&#8217;m doing a bit of traveling myself, and there are quite a few blogs out there devoted to just travel. Maybe you want to start a travel blog yourself. If you do, here are four free <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/\">WordPress</a> themes to get you started.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11092\" title=\"screenshot\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/adventure-journal\"><strong>Adventure Journal</strong></a> is a powerful, feature-rich theme that lets you customize a wide variety of features from the comfort of your Dashboard.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11093\" title=\"screenshot-1\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/beach\"><strong>Beach</strong></a> brings the warm feel of Thailand’s shores to your blog year round.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11094\" title=\"screenshot-2\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/themes/travel-blogger\"><strong>Travel Blogger</strong></a> offers travelers a highly customizable, very easy to use travel blog theme that offers 2 gorgeous default skins.</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-11095\" title=\"screenshot-3\" src=\"http://weblogtoolscollection.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/screenshot-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" 