 feature, optional extra fields, and an option to redirect visitors to any URL after the message is sent.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.faktor.cc/Fotomobil/wp-osm-plugin\"><strong>OSM</strong></a> displays maps in your WordPress blog using the OpenLayers technology.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/widget-logic-visual/\"><strong>Widget Logic Visual</strong></a> lets you control on which pages widgets appear using conditional tags.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/qjUAevaUXwA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 14:00:44 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:5:\"James\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:1530:\"<h3>New plugins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.believersresource.com/downloads/verse-links-102.html\"><strong>Verse Links</strong></a> searches for Bible verse references within blog posts or comments and links them to a reference site of your choice.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wp-piwik/\"><strong>WP-Piwik</strong></a> adds a Piwik stats site to your dashboard.</p>\n<h3>Updated plugins</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/backwpup/\"><strong>BackWPup</strong></a> allows you to backup your WordPress database, files, and more.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/cleverness-to-do-list/\"><strong>Cleverness To-Do List</strong></a> integrates a customizable, multi-featured to-do list.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.fastsecurecontactform.com/\"><strong>Fast Secure Contact Form</strong></a> lets your visitors send you a quick e-mail message and blocks all common spammer tactics. Additionally, the plugin has a multi-form feature, optional extra fields, and an option to redirect visitors to any URL after the message is sent.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.faktor.cc/Fotomobil/wp-osm-plugin\"><strong>OSM</strong></a> displays maps in your WordPress blog using the OpenLayers technology.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/widget-logic-visual/\"><strong>Widget Logic Visual</strong></a> lets you control on which pages widgets appear using conditional tags.</p>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/weblogtoolscollection/UXMP/~4/qjUAevaUXwA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";}i:12;a:7:{s:5:\"title\";s:56:\"WPTavern: Absolute Privacy Plugin Back In The Repository\";s:4:\"guid\";s:31:\"http://www.wptavern.com/?p=6344\";s:4:\"link\";s:108:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/mgsavUgVDqU/absolute-privacy-plugin-back-in-the-repository\";s:11:\"description\";s:1328:\"<p>A few days ago, <a href=\"http://blog.sucuri.net/2012/02/vulnerability-in-the-absolute-privacy-plugin.html\">Sucuri mentioned</a> that the Absolute Privacy plugin for WordPress contained a security vulnerability that would allow the ability to bypass the authentication mechanism and gain admin access to the application, that being WordPress. The plugin was subsequently pulled from the repository as there had not been any updates to fix the security issue for well over a year. Today however, the plugin can be found within the <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/absolute-privacy/\">repository again</a> as the security issue has now been fixed. </p>\n<p>Related posts:<ol>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.wptavern.com/absolute-privacy-plugin-now-at-v1-2\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Absolute Privacy Plugin Now At v1.2\">Absolute Privacy Plugin Now At v1.2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.wptavern.com/plugin-code-repository-bookmarklet\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Plugin Code Repository Bookmarklet\">Plugin Code Repository Bookmarklet</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.wptavern.com/plugin-repository-now-supports-videos\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Plugin Repository Now Supports Videos\">Plugin Repository Now Supports Videos</a></li>\n</ol></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~4/mgsavUgVDqU\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" />\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Mon, 27 Feb 2012 14:00:04 +0000\";s:2:\