ent to you all the information helpful to you. You can submit your problems to us.\r\nWish us all the best in our honest efforts !!!','Introduction',0,'','inherit','open','open','','5-revision-38','','','2009-02-21 05:02:36','2009-02-21 12:02:36','',5,'http://www.rightprocedure.org/?p=187',0,'revision','',0),(88,2,'2008-12-09 07:51:06','2008-12-09 14:51:06','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: Calibri;\">It was when my mom was diagnosed with Cancer that we felt the need to know the right procedure to claim Medical Insurance. I asked my colleagues, some said it was easy, some said I have to be careful with agents and some said it isn’t worth all the effort that we put in.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: Calibri;\">I got all sorts of information but didn’t get the right procedure or say the real picture. Now here started the journey to the unexplored. I called up my Insurance agent at the around 11 pm one night and asked him that it was a Corporate medical insurance, so what would be the ideal way to go about it.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><!--more--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: Calibri;\">Okay I say “go about it” and not “claiming it” because you do not necessarily claim the money when you have a medical or health insurance.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: small; font-family: Calibri;\">There are two ways to “go about it”; I was enlightened, which are as follows:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; line-height: 115%;\">Cashless</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">- You can avail this 