 and submitted. The form is called Tenant Information form and is available online at this address: </span>\r\n<div class=\"ajy\"><img id=\":2ii\" class=\"ajz\" src=\"https://mail.google.com/mail/u/0/images/cleardot.gif\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.punepolice.gov.in/pdf/PERSONAL_INFORMATION_OF_TENANT.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.punepolice.gov.in/pdf/PERSONAL_INFORMATION_OF_TENANT.pdf</a>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>You need to download the form, take a printout and fill up all the required details.</li>\r\n	<li>You need to paste your recent photograph on the form.</li>\r\n	<li>Get 2 photocopies of the form after you have filled in all the information.</li>\r\n	<li>You need to get a photocopy of your rent agreement</li>\r\n	<li>Get a letter from your employer, if employed.</li>\r\n	<li>You need to get a photocopy of an Identity proof- pan card or driving license.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAll these documents have to be submitted to the nearest police station and get them signed by the Inspector in charge. The officer also has to stamp the 2 copies of the form.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nNow one of these two stamped forms has to be given to the house owner and the other has to be kept with you for further reference.\r\n\r\nThis is the procedure followed in pune.\r\n\r\nIf you are reading this article and you are not from pune, please let us know the procedure followed in your city to keep record of tenants/owners.','Tenant information form',0,'','publish','open','open','','tenant-information-form-for-pune-police','','','2012-02-29 04:40:07','2012-02-29 11:40:07','',0,'http://www.rightprocedure.com/?p=126',0,'post','',0),(127,1,'2008-12-16 21:25:36','2008-12-17 04:25:36','Its need to be submitted to pune police.\nyou can get it online here.\n\n<a href=\"http://www.punepolice.com/Circular.htm\">http://www.punepolice.com/Circular.htm</a>\n\nyou need to download the form, take printout, write  all information\n<ol>\n	<li>you need to paste your recent photo on form.</li>\n